etsysMibOrg.description: This MIB module defines a portion of the SNMP enterprise MIBs under Enterasys Networks' enterprise OID. This module defines OBJECT-IDENTIFIER(s) to be used for the registration of MODULE-IDENTITY in all Enterasys Networks' MIB modules. The naming of OIDs should be based upon the name of the MODULE-IDENTITY for which they are the base OID. For example, if the MODULE-IDENTITY for the MIB is fooBarMIB then the OBJECT IDENTIFIER should be named fooBarOID. All Enterasys MIBs should follow the format specified by enterasys-mib-template.txt.
